V0115_01_00_00_0.text: Sweet! I can't wait to check out how your deck works!

V0115_01_00_01_0.text: No matter what monster you summon, I'm gonna Duel my Duel!

V0115_01_00_02_0.text: My HERO Deck is way better than before.

V0115_01_00_03_1.text: Until one of us comes out on top!

V0115_01_00_04_0.text: I'm not planning on going easy on ya.

V0115_01_00_04_1.text: I'm goin' all out from the start!

V0115_01_00_05_0.text: Chazz! I know you're no pushover, so stop acting like one!

V0115_01_00_06_0.text: Alexis, it's been a while since we've Dueled like this.

V0115_01_00_07_0.text: Sy, did you finally build a deck that's all about you?

V0115_01_00_09_0.text: I'll show ya what I learned these past three years, Teach!

V0115_01_00_10_0.text:
Let's Duel, Jesse!
Win or lose, it'll be fun!

V0115_01_00_11_0.text: Yubel, I promise to get you back!

V0115_01_00_12_0.text:
Sartorius!
I'm gonna do what I gotta do, whatever it takes!

V0115_01_00_14_0.text: I heard the King of Games had another side to him.

V0115_01_00_14_1.text:
And that must be you!
The Pharaoh!

V0115_01_00_15_0.text: I know you love Duel Monsters as much as me!

V0115_01_00_15_1.text: Let's get our game on, Yusei!

V0115_03_00_04_0.text: You shoulda defeated me, and now you're gonna pay!

V0115_03_00_05_0.text: This Duel is only getting started!

V0115_05_00_00_0.text: I almost forgot that I'm not Dueling alone!

V0115_06_01_02_0.text: Just what I was waiting for!

I activate my Equip Spell!
Rainbow Veil!

V0115_08_00_26_0.text: My monster buddies and I have an unbreakable bond!

I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Super Polymerization!

I activate my Spell Card!

I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Flash Fusion!

I activate my Spell Card!

Soar!
Elemental HERO Shining Flare Wingman!

Neos and Yubel!

Elemental HERO Honest Neos!

V0115_13_00_53_0.text: We went through a lot so that we could stand here together.

V0115_13_00_55_0.text: Yubel's ultimate form lives within me!

V0115_16_00_00_0.text:
This Duel was fun!
But it all has to come to an end!

V0115_16_00_01_0.text:
This Duel was fun!
But it all has to come to an end!

V0115_19_00_06_0.text: Go and get 'em, Shining Flare Wingman!

V0115_21_00_00_0.text:
Seems like things are looking up for me!
I end my turn!

V0115_21_00_04_0.text:
I can't let my guard down for a sec!
I end my turn!

V0115_28_00_02_0.text: I couldn't have won without my monsters!

V0115_28_00_03_1.text: Not when I'm fighting for someone who's in my heart!

V0115_28_00_04_0.text: Umm... Are you pretending to be a slacker?

V0115_28_00_05_0.text: There's something I want to tell you...

V0115_28_00_05_1.text:
Thanks for a sweet Duel!
Now and forever!

V0115_28_00_06_0.text: Did you just copy your brother's deck?

V0115_28_00_06_1.text: You'll never win 'til you play your own game, Sy.

V0115_28_00_07_1.text: Looks like I finally passed the test, Dr. Crowler!

V0115_28_00_08_0.text: We have to fight against the Light of Destruction.

V0115_28_00_09_0.text: C'mon, no one can control fate!

V0115_28_00_09_1.text: You should know that more than anyone, Sartorius!

V0115_28_00_10_0.text:
Yugi, I'll never forget this Duel!
It's the best gift ever!

V0115_28_00_11_0.text: Yusei, I didn't think you were the type to give up.

V0115_29_00_00_0.text: I had no clue on what strategies you were gonna play!

V0115_29_00_01_0.text: I don't like losing, but I'd rather have a fun Duel!

V0115_29_00_02_1.text: Me and my HEROES will win in the end!

V0115_29_00_03_0.text: Sure, I might not be the strongest.

V0115_29_00_03_1.text: But that doesn't mean I'm not gonna fight!

V0115_29_00_04_0.text:
See, Chazz?
You can win without using silly tricks.

V0115_29_00_05_0.text: I never would've gotten this far without ya.

V0115_29_00_05_1.text: So I'm glad we got to know each other, Alexis!

V0115_29_00_06_0.text: Your deck wanted to win as badly as you, Sy!

V0115_29_00_07_0.text: You sure evolved right past me, Hassleberry!

V0115_29_00_08_0.text: I may not have shown it, but I learned a lot from ya, Teach!

V0115_29_00_09_0.text: Yeah, I sometimes get frustrated when I lose.

V0115_29_00_09_1.text: But that doesn't take the joy out of Dueling!

V0115_29_00_10_0.text:
I know the pain you endured.
Let's not Duel like that again.

V0115_29_00_11_0.text: Don't let the emptiness control you, Sartorius!

V0115_29_00_12_0.text:
Yugi, I'll get stronger!
So I hope we can Duel again!

V0115_29_00_13_0.text: Your moves are super sweet, Yusei!

V0115_30_00_00_0.text: Those silly moves won't work on me.

V0115_30_00_01_0.text: Wow, you have a lot of tricks.

V0115_30_00_02_0.text: What's the point of winning if you don't give it your all?

V0115_33_00_00_0.text: I kinda have a cool power.

V0115_33_00_02_0.text: I'll give it my best shot!

V0115_34_00_01_0.text: I'll use the power of the shadows to defeat you!

V0115_34_00_02_0.text: This is the best Duel I've had in a long time!

V0115_34_00_03_0.text: If this can't fire you up, you're no Duelist!

V0115_34_00_04_0.text: This Duel will remind me of what I've lost...

V0115_34_00_05_0.text: I have a bigger mission than this!

V0115_35_00_00_0.text: Just give it your all in every Duel!

V0115_35_00_01_0.text: There's someone inside me who believes in me!

V0115_36_00_01_0.text: I know you can handle this.

V0115_36_00_02_0.text: My bad. Hope you can get your game on!

V0115_36_00_03_0.text:
You got this, Alexis!
Just be careful of facedown cards.

V0115_27_00_00_0.text: I won't go down that easily!

V0115_01_00_16_0.text: The Supreme King is the darkness that lives in my soul.

V0115_28_00_12_0.text: The Supreme King and Yubel are both alive inside me!

V0115_29_00_14_0.text:
Argh...
My dark side is really tough!
